"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-113","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"无论如何，你都需要投入一定的时间和精力，而投入的多少取决于你想达到的目标高度。"},"196":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-114","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"光有一纸大学文凭，工作不会自己送上门来。"},"197":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-115","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"像 Google、Facebook 这样的公司，每年都会收到数以百万计的求职申请。"},"198":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-116","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"如果一家公司只录取 10% 的申请人，你的「求职资料包」就得胜过剩下 90% 的人。"},"199":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-117","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"很多时候，质量比数量更重要。"},"200":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-118","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"你可能海投 400 份简历，却依然毫无进展。"},"201":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-119","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"很多时候，通过招聘会建立的正确人脉、找到合适的岗位、做出有分量的副业项目、发出恰到好处的一条推文，或者获得前同事的推荐，这些途径的效果都比海投简历高出百倍。"},"202":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-120","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"充分准备是关键。"},"203":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-121","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"了解面试的流程并进行练习，提前准备好向面试官提的问题，以及一些交流要点——都能让你的面试通过率大幅提升。"},"204":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-122","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"如果求职流程的某个环节出了问题，就要评估并改进它。"},"205":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-123","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"比如，你申请了很多公司却完全没有收到面试通知，那么你的简历可能比其他候选人竞争力弱，或者你投递的渠道本身质量很差。"},"206":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-124","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#把精力花在对职业有帮助的事上","content":"又比如，你的面试总是没通过，那你可能需要多做模拟面试，并复盘分析自己没通过的原因。"},"207":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/caddy-and-formbricks","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/caddy-and-formbricks","type":"page","content":"Formbricks 配置 Caddy 反代","tags":[],"url":"/notes/geek-lab/caddy-and-formbricks"},"208":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/caddy-and-formbricks-0","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/caddy-and-formbricks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/caddy-and-formbricks","content":"已经启动了 Formbricks 的 Docker 容器，可以通过公网访问 IP:3000"},"209":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/caddy-and-formbricks-1","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/caddy-and-formbricks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/caddy-and-formbricks","content":"但是我想实现 survey.ztm0929.cn 的域名访问。"},"210":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/formbricks","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/formbricks","type":"page","content":"Formbricks","tags":[],"url":"/notes/geek-lab/formbricks"},"211":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/formbricks-0","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/formbricks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/formbricks","content":"Formbricks 是一个开源的问卷构建框架"},"212":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/formbricks-1","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/formbricks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/formbricks","content":"https://formbricks.com/"},"213":{"id":"/n